Dec 17

This is at work.
We collecxt the most elementary tests of pair emission algorithm.
We start from generating sample
e+e---> Z --> mu+mu-
and adding pairs with MC tester. Many of these tests require intervention 
in the code.


------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To recompile from the start (fresh repository or some problems)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

go to TAUOLA
source configure.paths.sh

go to PHOTOS
./configure --with-hepmc=$HEPMCLOCATION --with-pythia8=$PYTHIALOCATION --with-mc-tester=$MCTESTERLOCATION --with-tauola=$TAUOLALOCATION
make
cd examples
./configure
make
cd testing
make
cd pairs
make clobber && make mc-tester.pairs.root

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
at new window (needed only once)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

cd PHOTOS
source configure.paths.sh
cd examples/testing/pairs
make clobber && make mc-tester.pairs.root

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
after changing code (to recompile libraries and if successful, run the test)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

cd PHOTOS/examples/testing/pairs
(cd ../../..; make) && make clobber && make mc-tester.pairs.root

  or

cd PHOTOS
make
cd examples/testing/pairs
make clobber && make mc-tester.pairs.root

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

